Package org.cst8288Lab2.dto

Class StudentCourseDTO

java.lang.Object
org.cst8288Lab2.dto.StudentCourseDTO
public class StudentCourseDTO extends Object
Data Transfer Object (DTO) class for student-course relationship. This class is used to transfer the association data between student and course layers without exposing the database directly.
